  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to p11-kit</title>

    <para>The <application>p11-kit</application> package Provides a way to load
    and enumerate PKCS #11 (a Cryptographic Token Interface Standard) modules.
    </para>

    &lfs70_checked;

